{"type": "article", "id": 18595, "title": "果汁包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-07T07:52:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 65, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104221thSGY5FziBpmPLWV.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这组果汁的白色包装纸上都有水果的蓝色印章，像是将柠檬、橙子等水果从侧面剖开，然后印在了上面，能够指示出对应的水果，非常独特。实际上它仅仅使用了一个简单的玻璃瓶和一张白色的说明纸，但具有怀旧气息的印章表达出了果汁天然和独特的概念。设计来自莫斯科的设计工作室 Nikita Ivanov 。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104216AOvNMlKj26r1xuFS.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060710421627wbiGJu0zkMN9xv.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104220qKFdMn095yPSzxwv.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071042200GCbm2qAjUp6Q4e1.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}